    {
      "guid": "NDEyMDgzN3xWSVp8REFTSEJPQVJEfDQ3MDIwMTkw",
      "name": "Data Selection",
      "description": null,
      "widgets": [
        {
          "id": "523087685",
          "title": "",
          "layout": {
            "column": 1,
            "row": 1,
            "width": 2,
            "height": 4
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.markdown"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "text": "## Topics:\n* [WHERE logic](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/nrql-new-relic-query-language/get-started/nrql-syntax-clauses-functions/#sel-where)\n* [IN](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/nrql-new-relic-query-language/get-started/nrql-syntax-clauses-functions/#sel-where)\n* [LIKE](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/nrql-new-relic-query-language/get-started/nrql-syntax-clauses-functions/#sel-where)\n* [IS (NOT) NULL](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/nrql-new-relic-query-language/get-started/nrql-syntax-clauses-functions/#sel-where)\n* [Casting with numeric()](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/nrql-new-relic-query-language/get-started/nrql-syntax-clauses-functions/#type-conversion)\n* [RLIKE regex](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/nrql-new-relic-query-language/get-started/nrql-syntax-clauses-functions/#sel-where) uses: [Re2 Syntax](https://github.com/google/re2/wiki/Syntax)\n* [Regex Capture](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/nrql-new-relic-query-language/get-started/nrql-syntax-clauses-functions/#func-capture)\n* [Filter()](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/nrql-new-relic-query-language/get-started/nrql-syntax-clauses-functions/#func-filter) and [Percentage()](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/nrql-new-relic-query-language/get-started/nrql-syntax-clauses-functions/#func-percentage)\n* [Multiple data sources](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/nrql-new-relic-query-language/get-started/nrql-syntax-clauses-functions/#state-select)\n* List [data types](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/nrql-new-relic-query-language/get-started/nrql-syntax-clauses-functions/#show-event-types) and [attributes](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/nrql-new-relic-query-language/get-started/nrql-syntax-clauses-functions/#keyset)\n* [Filter by time](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/nrql-new-relic-query-language/get-started/nrql-syntax-clauses-functions/#sel-since)\n\n## Other references\n* [New Relic attribute dictionary](https://docs.newrelic.com/attribute-dictionary/)\n* [Re2 Syntax](https://github.com/google/re2/wiki/Syntax)"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087686",
          "title": "WHERE Clause  by value",
          "layout": {
            "column": 3,
            "row": 1,
            "width": 2,
            "height": 4
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.table"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "dataFormatters": [],
            "facet": {
              "showOtherSeries": false
            },
            "nrqlQueries": [
              {
                "accountId": "${account_id}",
                "query": "SELECT count(*) from Transaction facet appName where appName='${apm_appname}' or (appName='${apm_appname2}' and appName = '${apm_appname3}')\n"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087687",
          "title": "Dealing with NULL / NOT NULL",
          "layout": {
            "column": 5,
            "row": 1,
            "width": 2,
            "height": 4
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.table"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "dataFormatters": [],
            "facet": {
              "showOtherSeries": false
            },
            "nrqlQueries": [
              {
                "accountId": "${account_id}",
                "query": "SELECT http.statusCode  from Transaction where http.statusCode != 200 and http.statusCode is not null"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087688",
          "title": "Casting strings to numbers with numeric()",
          "layout": {
            "column": 7,
            "row": 1,
            "width": 2,
            "height": 4
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.table"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "dataFormatters": [],
            "facet": {
              "showOtherSeries": false
            },
            "nrqlQueries": [
              {
                "accountId": "${account_id}",
                "query": "SELECT count(*) from Transaction where http.statusCode is not null facet http.statusCode where numeric(http.statusCode) !=200"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087689",
          "title": "Simple regular expression with RLIKE",
          "layout": {
            "column": 9,
            "row": 1,
            "width": 2,
            "height": 4
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.table"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "dataFormatters": [],
            "facet": {
              "showOtherSeries": false
            },
            "nrqlQueries": [
              {
                "accountId": "${account_id}",
                "query": "SELECT uniques(appName) from Transaction where appName rlike '[C].+'"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087690",
          "title": "RLIKE Example 2",
          "layout": {
            "column": 11,
            "row": 1,
            "width": 2,
            "height": 4
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.table"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "dataFormatters": [],
            "facet": {
              "showOtherSeries": false
            },
            "nrqlQueries": [
              {
                "accountIds": [
                  "${account_id}"
                ],
                "query": "select browserTransactionName from PageView where browserTransactionName rlike r'.*${domain_name}.*'"
              }
            ],
            "platformOptions": {
              "ignoreTimeRange": false
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087691",
          "title": "Basic aparse()",
          "layout": {
            "column": 1,
            "row": 5,
            "width": 2,
            "height": 3
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.table"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "dataFormatters": [],
            "facet": {
              "showOtherSeries": false
            },
            "nrqlQueries": [
              {
                "accountIds": [
                  "${account_id}"
                ],
                "query": "FROM PageView\nSELECT aparse(browserTransactionName, '%${domain_name}:443/*') as example "
              }
            ],
            "platformOptions": {
              "ignoreTimeRange": false
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087692",
          "title": "aparse Advanced",
          "layout": {
            "column": 3,
            "row": 5,
            "width": 2,
            "height": 3
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.table"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "dataFormatters": [],
            "facet": {
              "showOtherSeries": false
            },
            "nrqlQueries": [
              {
                "accountIds": [
                  "${account_id}"
                ],
                "query": "WITH aparse(message, '%userId=*,%productId=*,%quantity=*') as (userId, productId, quantity)\nFROM Log \nSELECT userId, productId, quantity\nWHERE userId IS NOT NULL"
              }
            ],
            "platformOptions": {
              "ignoreTimeRange": false
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087693",
          "title": "REGEX  Capture",
          "layout": {
            "column": 5,
            "row": 5,
            "width": 2,
            "height": 3
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.table"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "dataFormatters": [],
            "facet": {
              "showOtherSeries": false
            },
            "nrqlQueries": [
              {
                "accountId": "${account_id}",
                "query": "\nSELECT count(*) from Transaction where appName like '%Service' limit max facet capture(appName,r'(?P<service>.*)Service')\n"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087694",
          "title": "Capture example 2",
          "layout": {
            "column": 7,
            "row": 5,
            "width": 2,
            "height": 3
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.table"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "dataFormatters": [],
            "facet": {
              "showOtherSeries": false
            },
            "nrqlQueries": [
              {
                "accountId": "${account_id}",
                "query": "SELECT count(*) from Transaction where appName like '%Service' limit max facet capture(appName,r'(pr1)?-?(?P<service>.*)Service')"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087695",
          "title": "Capture simplify data example",
          "layout": {
            "column": 9,
            "row": 5,
            "width": 4,
            "height": 3
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.table"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "dataFormatters": [],
            "facet": {
              "showOtherSeries": false
            },
            "nrqlQueries": [
              {
                "accountIds": [
                  "${account_id}"
                ],
                "query": "select  capture(browserTransactionName,r'.*${domain_name}:443(?P<name>.*)'), browserTransactionName from PageView where browserTransactionName rlike r'.*${domain_name}.*'\n"
              }
            ],
            "platformOptions": {
              "ignoreTimeRange": false
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087696",
          "title": "",
          "layout": {
            "column": 1,
            "row": 8,
            "width": 12,
            "height": 1
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.markdown"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "text": "# Filtering data within the same query\nThis is useful for calculating percentages and comparing subsets of data all within one query."
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087697",
          "title": "Using filter()",
          "layout": {
            "column": 1,
            "row": 9,
            "width": 3,
            "height": 3
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.table"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "dataFormatters": [],
            "facet": {
              "showOtherSeries": false
            },
            "nrqlQueries": [
              {
                "accountId": "${account_id}",
                "query": "SELECT average(duration) as 'all', filter(average(duration), where name like '%GetCart') as 'GetCart Avg', filter(count(*), where name like '%GetCart') as 'GetCart Count' from Transaction where appName='Cart Service'"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087698",
          "title": "Filter() for percentage",
          "layout": {
            "column": 4,
            "row": 9,
            "width": 4,
            "height": 3
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.table"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "dataFormatters": [],
            "facet": {
              "showOtherSeries": false
            },
            "nrqlQueries": [
              {
                "accountId": "${account_id}",
                "query": "SELECT count(*) as 'all',  filter(count(*), where name like '%GetCart') as 'GetCart Count', (filter(count(*), where name like '%GetCart') / count(*) * 100) as 'percent GetCart'  from Transaction where appName='Cart Service'\n"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087699",
          "title": "Using Percentage() for percentages instead of filter",
          "layout": {
            "column": 8,
            "row": 9,
            "width": 5,
            "height": 3
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.table"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "dataFormatters": [],
            "facet": {
              "showOtherSeries": false
            },
            "nrqlQueries": [
              {
                "accountId": "${account_id}",
                "query": "SELECT count(*) as 'all',  filter(count(*), where name like '%GetCart') as 'GetCart Count', (filter(count(*), where name like '%GetCart') / count(*) * 100) as 'percent GetCart' , percentage(count(*), where name like '%GetCart') as 'percent GetCart' from Transaction where appName='Cart Service'\n"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087700",
          "title": "",
          "layout": {
            "column": 1,
            "row": 12,
            "width": 12,
            "height": 1
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
            "id": "viz.markdown"
          },
          "rawConfiguration": {
            "text": "# Data sources and Attributes\nYou can select data from multiple event types. You can also query what  event types are available and find out what attributes they have. Checkout the data dictionary to understand New Relic event attributes."
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "523087701",
          "title": "Select from multiple tables",
          "layout": {
            "column": 1,
            "row": 13,
            "width": 2,
            "height": 3
          },
          "linkedEntityGuids": null,
          "visualization": {
